{"tid":1995783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人連好勝心都失去埋？","createTime":"2020-04-30T13:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T20:53:45.000Z","uid":201604,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0fb0b7ce063461e23a444f04ddec8c6d0f4fba","tid":1995783,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:33:01.000Z","msg":"以前好鍾意贏 贏到人 有人讚 會好開心<br />\n想自己榜上有名 做咩都會放好多時間心力落去<br />\n連上連登都要做最撚煩嗰個 要個個都記得我<br />\n<br />\n但今日先發現 就算畀你拎到第一又點<br />\n都改變唔到啲咩<br />\n就算幾努力都冇用<br />\n就算做到啲乜都冇用<br />\n做咩都冇用<br />\n<br />\n已經咩都唔想做 唔想知 唔想理<br />\n唔好煩到我<br />\n個心好攰 個身都好攰<br />\n繼續存在又冇意思 做咩都唔開心"},{"pid":"b69e7da9c7d89cbb180d5f5117dd143c20f1f8bb","tid":1995783,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e5483f57ac5d4eacfb97ab60a5b8681216554f","tid":1995783,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69e7da9c7d89cbb180d5f5117dd143c20f1f8bb","tid":1995783,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔好睇我post 會影響你溫書心情"},{"pid":"38c5dcdba76879dfa205e1091248a666f79c13f6","tid":1995783,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e5483f57ac5d4eacfb97ab60a5b8681216554f","tid":1995783,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69e7da9c7d89cbb180d5f5117dd143c20f1f8bb","tid":1995783,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔好睇我post 會影響你溫書心情"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"本身都無心機"},{"pid":"38de1664a68cb4b227c7aeedca70a0f1d0b0f4ed","tid":1995783,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":